      "index": 208,
      "text": "概念模型设计",
      "style": "Heading 3",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 209,
      "text": "依据系统需求分析，本文对系统进行概念模型设计。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 210,
      "text": "本系统的数据库设计以中医体质信息采集子系统的需求为基础，进行中医体质信息分析时，则以原有数据库为基础，增加概念分层表，使得：在不改变数据库结构情况下，能够对多种因素进行分析。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 211,
      "text": "本系统主要涉及的实体包括：用户、中医体质判定标准和中医体质；其中，",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 8,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 212,
      "text": "（1）用户实体：用户编号、姓名、性别、民族、出生日期、身高、体重、BMI、所在省份、电话号码、职业、工作单位、既往病史、现病史。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 213,
      "text": "（2）中医体质判定标准实体：问题编号、问题内容、标准标号、标准名称。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 214,
      "text": "（3）中医体质实体：体质编号、体质名称、体质特征、形体特征、常见表现、心理特征、发病倾向、对外界环境适应能力。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 215,
      "text": "根据上述实体，本文设计了系统概念模型E-R图，如图4-6所示。",
