      "style": "Heading 2",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 243,
      "text": "本系统开发环境为WAMP，即操作系统采用Windows10，Web服务器为Apache，数据库采用MySQL数据库，系统开发语言采用PHP。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 9,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 244,
      "text": "另外，系统开发软件为WampServer64和Dreamweaver，多维分析实现部分采用Tableau Software工具来创建多个中医体质分析图。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 10,
