      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 251,
      "text": "PHP开发语言",
      "style": "Heading 3",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 3,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 252,
      "text": "PHP是一种被广泛应用在服务器端的脚本语言。PHP与C语言的风格类似，有着独特的开发特性，它的优势就是可以嵌入到服务器端的XTML脚本文件中，不需要单独编写代码文件，使开发网页的效率大大提高。网页制作的本质是超文本标记语言，作为预处理器的…",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 253,
      "text": "在系统中，客户端的浏览器发送请求给Web服务器，Web服务器调用PHP程序来完成指定的工作。PHP程序的执行主要是完成对数据库的操作，然后会返回执行结果给Web服务器，Web服务器解释执行后，最终将相对应的结果返回到客户端。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 254,
      "text": "Apache服务器",
      "style": "Heading 3",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 4,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 255,
      "text": "Apache服务器是由一个非营利性机构发布的一种开源服务器，允许任何人修改其中的错误，但是前提是要通过所有的审核和测试。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 3,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 256,
      "text": "Apache的主要特点在于：",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 257,
      "text": "可以简单快捷的配置文件；",
      "style": "List Paragraph",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 4,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 258,
      "text": "Apache虚拟机可以写成过滤器形式；",
      "style": "List Paragraph",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 4,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 259,
      "text": "本地Windows NT Unicode提供多语言支持；",
      "style": "List Paragraph",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 4,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 260,
      "text": "能够更好地支持非Unix平台。",
      "style": "List Paragraph",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 4,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 4,
