    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 301,
      "text": "用户在主界面点击“体质测试”项，完成个人自然信息填写后点击【提交】按钮，或者在浏览器地址栏输入网址，均可以进入中医体质测试界面。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 3,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 302,
      "text": "该界面的所有问题都来源于《中医体质分类判定标准》，该标准在2009年由中华中医药学会发布，将中医体质分为九种类型，判定方法与判定标准，如下：",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 3,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 303,
      "text": "（1）判定方法",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 304,
      "text": "回答《中医体质分类与判定表》中的全部问题，每一个问题按5级评分，计算原始分和转化分，依标准判定体质类型。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 305,
      "text": "原始分=各个条目的分值相加。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 306,
      "text": "转化分数=[(原始分-条目数)/(条目数*4)]*100",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 4,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 307,
      "text": "（2）判定标准",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 308,
      "text": "平和质为正常体质，其他8种体质为偏颇体质。判定标准如表5-1所示。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 3,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
