      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 432,
      "text": "本系统采用黑盒测试法，测试计划如下：",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 433,
      "text": "（1）界面测试",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 434,
      "text": "系统通过界面与用户进行交互，本系统的界面测试用于测试中医体质信息采集与分析系统的各个模块的布局是否合理，系统界面的控件操作是否便捷，界面的相关介绍内容是否简单易懂。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 435,
      "text": "（2）功能测试",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 3,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 436,
      "text": "功能测试主要进行系统各个模块的测试，包括系统自然信息录入功能测试、中医体质判定功能测试、中医体质判定结果测试和中医体质分析测试。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 437,
