      "style": "Heading 2",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 438,
      "text": "界面测试",
      "style": "Heading 3",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 439,
      "text": "为了保证系统界面与用户具有良好的交互性，测试角度如下：",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 440,
      "text": "易用性。本系统将具有同一功能的控件位置集中，方便用户操作。本系统的界面进行了分区域块划分，控件位置明显，较少的使用下拉条。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 7,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 441,
      "text": "合理性。比较重要的按钮放在明显的位置，系统提示和警告均会在界面中央弹出提示框或警告框。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 7,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 442,
      "text": "美观与协调性。本系统布局合理，页面设置既不紧密，也不空旷，合理利用了系统空间。本系统的按钮大小基本相近，与界面大小相协调。本系统背景颜色搭配合理，反差不大，界面风格保持一致。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 7,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
